  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  hip arthroscopy

          -  ages 18-80

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  history of neurological disease

          -  diabetes

          -  pregnancy

          -  neuropathy

          -  chronic narcotic use

          -  allergy to local anesthetic solution

          -  inability to give consent or cooperate with the study protocol
      </textblock>
